1. Autonomous navigation
  •SLAM is a unique mixture of sensing the nearby environment while creating a virtual map of helpful information.
  •The fact that we are moving our robot will force us to sense the environment in real-time, and it would be exciting to see the bot work while we can see what the bot sees through its eyes.
2. Hexapod
  •Synchronized motion of the bot and mobility control of its legs to ensure the motion we want is what is taking place.
  •Developing a robot is exciting and enough reason to work on it.
